-- Thomas Cook Hires Credit Suisse to Sell Indian Unit, Times Says
-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 2012-02-05T09:13:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-05/thomas-cook-hires-credit-suisse-to-sell-indian-unit-times-says.html
Thomas Cook Group Plc (TCG)  hired  Credit
Suisse Group AG (CSGN)  to help to sell its Indian foreign exchange
unit, the London-based Sunday Times  reported  without citing
anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduard Gismatullin in London at 
